e'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Gatsby loaded images\"\n        title=\"Gatsby loaded images\"\n        src=\"/static/7201838ca7a0df22ef9909ecfa8d9d3b/dbb61/2019-11-25%2006-fancy-image-loaded.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/7201838ca7a0df22ef9909ecfa8d9d3b/19bd1/2019-11-25%2006-fancy-image-loaded.png 163w,\n/static/7201838ca7a0df22ef9909ecfa8d9d3b/d3bcb/2019-11-25%2006-fancy-image-loaded.png 325w,\n/static/7201838ca7a0df22ef9909ecfa8d9d3b/dbb61/2019-11-25%2006-fancy-image-loaded.png 650w,\n/static/7201838ca7a0df22ef9909ecfa8d9d3b/6b691/2019-11-25%2006-fancy-image-loaded.png 975w,\n/static/7201838ca7a0df22ef9909ecfa8d9d3b/91670/2019-11-25%2006-fancy-image-loaded.png 1300w,\n/static/7201838ca7a0df22ef9909ecfa8d9d3b/99445/2019-11-25%2006-fancy-image-loaded.png 1908w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>One does need to load the images slightly different now, however thats a minor price to pay for all the features we gain.</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Day 35"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/day35/"}}}